---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';

import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Software Support and Maintenance Guide">
    <Nav />

    <main class="max-w-screen-xl block mx-auto mt-16 p-8">
        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">How We Support You</h2>
            <div class="prose prose-lg">
                <p class="mb-6">
                    NidoSoft is dedicated to delivering exceptional support, ensuring the seamless operation of your software. Our support services include:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
                    <li><strong>24/7 Customer Assistance</strong>: Our support team is available around the clock to address your inquiries and resolve issues promptly.</li>
                    <li><strong>Regular Updates</strong>: Stay up-to-date with the latest software enhancements, security patches, and feature releases.</li>
                    <li><strong>Proactive Monitoring</strong>: We employ advanced monitoring tools to identify and address potential issues before they impact your operations.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Software Maintenance Guidelines</h2>
            <div class="prose prose-lg">
                <p class="mb-6">
                    Our priority is to ensure the longevity and optimal performance of your software. Our software maintenance guidelines encompass:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
                    <li><strong>Regular Updates</strong>: Receive timely updates to address bugs, enhance features, and maintain compatibility with evolving technologies.</li>
                    <li><strong>Security Patching</strong>: Protect your software from vulnerabilities with our proactive approach to security patching.</li>
                    <li><strong>Performance Optimization</strong>: We continuously optimize code for improved performance, responsiveness, and scalability.</li>
                    <li><strong>Documentation</strong>: Access comprehensive documentation for troubleshooting, configuration, and best practices.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Contact Us for Support and Maintenance</h2>
            <div class="prose prose-lg">
                <p class="mb-6">
                    Connect with us to initiate support requests, discuss maintenance plans, or inquire about our services:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
                    <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@nidosoft.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@nidosoft.com</a></li>
                    <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+1234567890" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">+1 (234) 567-890</a></li>
                    <li>Support Portal: Visit our <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Support Portal</a> for a personalized experience.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>

